{"tid":1591030,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"屌你老母 成個熱門都係民陣洗左廿幾萬買音響","createTime":"2019-09-24T03:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T08:06:35.000Z","uid":244617,"like":153,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad3923e10b17820b09a9c2c6e8fca959cf82181","tid":1591030,"uid":244617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:47:22.000Z","msg":"事實上係有不完美 要改善<br />\n但而家大家打緊杖呀 呢個時候比小小信任得唔得啊<br />\n屌你老母可以推到成版熱門都係<br />\n屌自己人就最撚大聲 買左廿幾萬音響係咪緊要過曬政府 黑警呢幾日做左咁多仆街野啊 <br />\n成撚日話要學藍絲咁就算講變歪理都不割席 不指責自己 但而家用左廿幾萬就個個癲鳩曬咁<br />\n黑警d核彈就沉撚曬<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打緊杖呀大老！</span><br />\n對準政權呀！"},{"pid":"f36bdba1513b12f2eb45865a78353861d10dc4c0","tid":1591030,"uid":244617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"088580898c9f1f4fa93911e070bc509d1798943a","tid":1591030,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:48:48.000Z","msg":"&lt;未FC不喜勿進&gt;暗網爆新屋嶺殺人黑材料<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1591022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1591022</a>"},{"pid":"727bfff43e01f14302ae8072fbd0f5fd6b457da1","tid":1591030,"uid":244617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6171a2bcf8aca35dc969e65e10da0eba932a8247","tid":1591030,"uid":244617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:50:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c37aeedf91be50c31fe07a403a255f9dece89b19","tid":1591030,"uid":244617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5dadd090d8d7a17da23c327b9dcd966ea98e499","tid":1591030,"uid":244617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:50:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c0da0f3800d06ffc8d1e8ae97d98afdaf0c32ce","tid":1591030,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h